messages.text: I went once with my dad.
I remember it being so nice after Oak smog zone.
Like, you could actually breathe up there.
We would roll down the windows and just smell the air.
Have to leave for restaurant in like 20. Can't talk long actually :(
My mom says to tell you we don’t need those tube things
Wow. Can't wait to hear about it.
I saw you texted her but she wouldn’t show me them Weirdly protective of her relationship with you
Don’t forget I have known her basically my entire life... I’ve put in my time!
My mom is taking me to a “quiet dinner” tonight So depressing
Anyway anyway anyway. You still there?
I only see him with you.
He was going to dinner with my mom and I tonight but canceled really suddenly
I think he's freaked by the leuk stuff
Plus how could he not be?
I’ve had two hip replacements and my hair is falling out. Sexy?
Honestly, nat? Honest truth? I’m just going to say it. My mom saw you and sam at safeway yesterday.
Don’t know -- wanted to respect ur privacy, I guess
So funny we were all there the same time !
Whatever. I know it shouldn't still make me jealous to hear about you guys together. It’s been so long since you guys had your thing
I can understand why it would.
So weird all this medical stuff.
My doc gave me this Rx
Have to be chopped into two they’re so strong
I hate thinking of you taking something like that.
I'm holding the whole bottle in my hand
You're the only person I've been able to talk about the real stuff with
I'm not that good at it.
... me included So much is hard to say
Wanna know how I really feel?
Chat window appears from SamtheMan to Natalie
This is going to be difficult
It’s possible this is her last bday
We set up the yurt with candles like you suggested.
It’s open right onto the water. The dolphins are out! Che romantique. ;)
You'll bring payment for the site? THX!
We have to stop at restaurant to pick up my check
At least acknowledge it’s her birthday So cruel not to
No! Don’t ruin everything last minute.
Shoot sorry getting ready to go – no time to parse all that. Will look later!
See you Saturday at Talia’s? Talk soon xx xx
I won't be there. I just logged on to say goodbye. By the time you read this, I will be a part of the universe. Love to you. Love to Sam. I'm glad you can be together. Really. I am. Bye.
Natalie will receive these messages when she next logs in.
Grace? Your mom says you didn’t show at dinner.

I hate to ruin the surprise but at this point... Sam and I threw you a surprise campout!!! We're all here. But no you? Sam's waiting for you in the love later! Wait, hang on, reading big paragraph above.
